        <ul class="text-base-content/70 text-sm space-y-2">
          <li>• <strong class="text-secondary">Job interviews:</strong> Don't appear too eager; suggest you're evaluating multiple opportunities</li>
          <li>• <strong class="text-secondary">Client relationships:</strong> Premium service providers are selective about clients</li>
          <li>• <strong class="text-secondary">Social events:</strong> The person who shows up to everything is less interesting than selective attendees</li>
